TML5 theme with 4 color schemes and some very interesting features (including new menus and caption layout block). Theme should be released in 2 weeks.</p>\n<p>Theme will feature new menu that is responsive, it will use Nivo Slider and it will support 2 sidebars with additional footer slider. Header for the theme will support two different layouts, with menu in line with logo, and with logo above menu (if you need to have longer menu).</p>\n<p>Theme will add additional layout block (called Caption) that will be located bellow header (and sort of part of the header). This block can have some predefine content (for archives or pages), or you can create it on your own using meta box added for it to posts.<br />\nIf everything goes OK (testing responsive theme can be tricky, due to many different screen sizes and devices), skyScape should be released in about 3 weeks.</p>\n<script src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~s/adsense@gdragon.info?i=http://www.dev4press.com/2013/blog/development/theme-coming-soon-skyscape/" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:79:"http://www.dev4press.com/2013/blog/development/theme-coming-soon-skyscape/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:10;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:81:"\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:39:"Coming Soon: GD Products Center Pro 1.2";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:1