211; <a title="SMART Plugins on CodeCanyon" href="http://d4p.me/ccp" target="_blank">CodeCanyon</a>. Right now, one plugin is released, 2 plugins are in development and 2 more are in early planning stages.</p>\n<p>First plugin released so far is <a href="http://d4p.me/ccsmw" target="_blank"><strong>Smart Market Widgets</strong></a>. Using this plugin you can add files and authors information and links from any Envato Marketplace to your website. Files can be displayed in different ways (thumbnails or details), with author information. Data can be retrieved from file collections, popular files, latest files. Featured authors and files are also supported. This plugin costs only $11.00.</p>\n<p>New plugins will be announced on Dev4Press when released.</p>\n<div class="xss-infobox xss-infobox-color-red"><h4>SMART Plugins:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Official Website: <a href="http://www.millan.rs/" target="_blank">www.millan.rs</a></li>\n<li>On CodeCanyon: <a href="http://d4p.me/ccp" target="_blank">codecanyon.net</a></li>\n</ul></div>\n<script src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~s/adsense@gdragon.info?i=http://www.dev4press.com/2012/blog/introducing-smart-plugins-project/" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:74:"http://www.dev4press.com/2012/blog/introducing-smart-plugins-project/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:22;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:63:"\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s: