(standard &#8211; subscription or lifetime) and you will get <strong>1 theme</strong> for free.</li>\n<li>Purchase any plugin (developer or enterprise) and you will get <strong>1 theme</strong> license for free.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>Have a great time, and Merry Christmas!</strong></span></p>\n<div class="xss-infobox xss-infobox-color-red"><strong>Notice</strong>: All gift licenses will be awarded automatically up to 24 hours after the purchase is processed and activated. Gifts are awarded only if you are eligible for them, they can&#8217;t be exchanged for something else. Gifts are not transferable to third party.</div>\n<script src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~s/adsense@gdragon.info?i=http://www.dev4press.com/2012/blog/promotions/christmas-2012-35-discount-and-gifts/" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:88:"http://www.dev4press.com/2012/blog/promotions/christmas-2012-35-discount-and-gifts/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:23;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:87:"\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"xScape Framework And Core 1.8.5";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:79:"http://www.dev4press.com/2012/blog/themes-news/xscape-framework-and-core-1-8-5/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_ba