b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"MillaN";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2027:"<p>This month Dev4Press celebrates third birthday. On December 15 2009, Dev4Press.com with premium plugins and support went online. Here is the short overview of Dev4Press past development, and at the end you can get special 20% discount to celebrate third birthday.</p>\n<p>Dev4Press has grown a lot over the past year, and right now there are 7 Premium plugins, 11 Free/Lite plugins, 1 Module (for GD Custom Posts And Taxonomies Tools Pro plugin), 11 themes and powerful xScape Theme Framework. Number of downloads has doubled this past year, and Dev4Press now works on 3 servers hosting main website and individual plugins websites.</p>\n<p>And, there are big plans for the future. Plugins remain priority, and while there are no plans for new Premium plugins, there will be at least one new free plugin released soon, there are plans for improving current Premium plugins further with focus on GD Products Center and GD Press Tools, modules for GD CPT Tools Pro will grow in number and GD Star Rating 2.0 is back on the right track. Few themes are in plans for the first half of 2013 with major updates to xScape Theme Framework.</p>\n<p>I would like to thank all Dev4Press users for their continued support and for working with me on improving Dev4Press for WordPress products. I am dedicated on delivering even more quality products for WordPress in the future.</p>\n<div class="xss-infobox xss-infobox-color-blue"><h3>Special 3 Years Celebration Discount Week</h3>\n<p>From today, December 12 2012 until the December 18 2012, you will get 20% discount for all our products. Discount coupon will be automatically applied to all purchase links and shopping cart on this website, but if you get to checkout page on ShareIt some other way, discount coupon to use is <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>THREEYEARS</strong></span>.</div>\n<script src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~s/adsense@gdragon.info?i=http://www.dev4press.com/2012/blog/announcements/three-years-of-dev4press/" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:79:"http://www.dev4press.com/2012/blog/announcements/three-years-of-dev4press/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"2";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:29;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:81:"\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n\n \n \n \n \n \n ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:44:"GD Custom Posts And Taxonomies Tools 4.0 Pro";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:93:"http://www.dev4press.com/2012/blog/plugins-news/gd-custom-posts-and-taxonomies-tools-4-0-pro/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:102:"http://www.dev4press.com/2012/blog/plugins-news/gd-custom-posts-and-taxonomies-tools-4-0-pro/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 11 Dec 2012 15:00:24 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"categor