/li>\n<li>Custom fields: user, post, period and email.</li>\n<li>Meta box groups to display multiple meta boxes at once using tabs.</li>\n<li>Many code improvements and refactoring of JavaScript.</li>\n<li>Improved custom fields data functions and objects.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>GD CPT Tools Pro 4.0 will be released on Monday. Hurry up and take advantage of the 20% discount, valid until Tuesday. Until new version is released, check out this video on using new meta boxes and custom fields:</p>\n<p><iframe width="500" height="281" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/qSiOUjCbz0w?fs=1&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>In the next few days there will be an announcement about few more modules planned for GD CPT Tools Pro. And as always, if you find any problems, please report them in the forums. This version makes many critical changes, that might break things, so any bug report is greatly appreciated.</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>Known issues:</strong> There are some bugs still expected, and few minor features are missing, and they will be fixed and added soon. Also, there is a potential conflict with GD Products Center due to use of same Units library, but plan is to release update to that plugin over the weekend.</p></blockquote>\n<div class="xss-infobox xss-infobox-color-blue"><h4>GD CPT Tools Pro Special Discount</h4>\n<p>For the next 10 days (ending December 11 2012), to celebrate soon to be released major 4.0 version, you can get 20% discount for this plugin, Index module or Dev4Press Plugins Pack by using coupon: <strong>GDCPTPRO4</strong> at the checkout on ShareIt.</div>\n<script src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~s/adsense@gdragon.info?i=http://www.dev4press.com/2012/blog/development/gd-custom-posts-and-taxonomies-tools-4-0-pro-rc-1/" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"com