ified in our<a title="Terms of Use" href="http://osw3go.ulisesmejias.com/2012/about/terms-of-use/">Terms of Use</a>, we reserve the right to edit all contributions.\r\n\r\n<strong>You must be 18 years of age to participate in this simulation.</strong>\r\n\r\nBy using this website, you indicate your consent to participate in this simulation and agree to the Terms of Use.\r\n<h3>Thank you for your participation.</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Informed Consent', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'informed-consent', '', '', '2013-05-21 09:05:40', '2013-05-21 09:05:40', '', 52, 'http://www.randybelcher.com/soap/?page_id=72', 0, 'page', '', 0);
