"http://osw3go.ulisesmejias.com/2012/about/terms-of-use/">Terms of Use</a>, we reserve the right to edit all contributions.\r\n\r\n<strong>You must be 18 years of age to participate in this simulation.</strong>\r\n\r\nBy using this website, you indicate your consent to participate in this simulation and agree to the Terms of Use.\r\n<h3>Thank you for your participation.</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Informed Consent', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '72-revision-4', '', '', '2013-02-19 18:28:34', '2013-02-19 18:28:34', '', 72, 'http://www.randybelcher.com/soap/2013/02/19/72-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
