 admin will record this info in your userprofile.\r\n\r\n<b id="internal-source-marker_0.204917166614905">Goal5 - User must complete one civic engagement project.\r\n</b>An ARG admin will record this info in your userprofile.<b id="internal-source-marker_0.204917166614905">\r\n</b>\r\n\r\nThe last three goals require you to engage in the ARG materials outside of the games website parameters. Attending other users events and creating your own events on campus will allow you to interact with other users in person. Conversations that were started in the comments section of a scenario post can be expanded upon and discussed in more detail. An admin of the ARG will be present to capture your attendance. This way, the ARG website will reflect your accomplished goal.\r\n\r\nAfter completion of all five goals, you are encouraged to stay involved on the ARG website, reading new posts in each scenario, and supporting other users who may just be starting out in the game.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ):</h2>\r\n1.<b id="internal-source-marker_0.204917166614905"> Who can join the ARG?\r\n</b>Only people with oswego.edu email address can join the ARG.<b id="internal-source-marker_0.204917166614905"></b>\r\n\r\n2.<strong> How do I know which articles in the ARG are real?\r\n</strong>None of the articles in the ARG are real. Please view the disclaimer and informed consent page for more information.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n3. <strong>Do the goals have to be accomplished in order? Or can I skip around?</strong>\r\nYou do not have to accomplish goals in a specific order.\r\n<b id="internal-source-marker_0.204917166614905">\r\n</b>4.<b id="internal-source-marker_0.204917166614905"> Can I add my own event and how do I do so?\r\n</b>You can add your own event by going to your user profile and clicking Events. Under the My Events tab, click the Add New button. Fill out the information and submit your event. <b id="internal-source-marker_0.204917166614905"></b>\r\n\r\n5. <strong>How do I change my profile information and avatar?</strong>\r\nYou can update your profile information by going to your user profile and clicking Profile. You can change your information under the Edit and Change Avatar tabs.<b id="internal-source-marker_0.204917166614905"></b>\r\n\r\n6. <strong>Do I have to read through all of Scenario 1 before moving on the Scenario 2 or can I skip around?</strong>\r\nYou do not have to read through each Scenario in order.', 'How to Play', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '177-revision-18', '', '', '2013-02-20 14:30:17', '2013-02-20 14:30:17', '', 177, 'http://www.randybelcher.com/soap/2013/02/20/177-revision-18/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
